* Sun Jun 07 2026 Shangyuxin <jiawa.syx@alibaba-inc.com> - 0.1.1-1
- `anolisa osbase sandbox install` provisions sandbox environments.
- `anolisa register` and `unregister` manage data-upload consent with 30-day deferral.
